Class AbstractDataRequestHandler

Direct Known Subclasses:
DataRequestHandler
public abstract class AbstractDataRequestHandler extends AbstractRequestHandler
Abstract base class for handling data exchange request messages. Provides common functionality for parsing entity kinds from DataRequestMsg payloads and updating GTNetEntity/GTNetConfigEntity states. Uses the ExchangeKindTypeRegistry for application-agnostic kind resolution. Subclasses should implement request validation and can override entity update behavior.
